Class LevelThree

java.lang.Object
java.util.Observable
Levels.LevelParent
Levels.LevelThree
public class LevelThree extends LevelParent
Represents the third level of the game. This level includes both a Boss and a MutationBoss1 as enemies. The level ends when the player defeats the MutationBoss1 or loses all their health.
